data.description: Elegant townhome in the heart of Nob Hill! This home features beautiful wood floors, spacious bedrooms and modern amenities, refrigerated air, granite counter, and designer details are just a few of the things that make this home so special. The natural light in this home is incredible! Enjoy the outside patio for indoor/outdoor entertaining. There are two balconies with great views! Nice size, 2 car garage with extra storage area! Walking distance to your local favorite restaurants, coffee houses and shops. HVAC and water heater replaced in 2021, outdoor stucco done this month. Washer, dryer and fridge will stay with this home!
